WEBVTT

30:17.691 --> 30:19.066
Under this beam here,

30:19.691 --> 30:20.691
on the wood...

30:20.941 --> 30:22.983
we could add
a mirror-work border.

30:23.149 --> 30:25.274
-We can do that.
-And then... a handrail...

30:25.441 --> 30:27.608
Wouldn't it be nice if we ran it
from here to there?
